{"tid":93864,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又死5隻]湖南炮竹倉庫起火連環爆　波及多車網傳5死","createTime":"2017-01-24T17:55:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-01T00:09:47.000Z","uid":32407,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5921a55a50a656725c41fcfe313acb575f57f9ad","tid":93864,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T17:55:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170125/bkncn-20170125000116415-0125_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170125%2Fbkncn-20170125000116415-0125_05011_001.html&d=qB95qSbxLZ8uPmKg0ty22AT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=1994db5e\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170125/bkncn-20170125000116415-0125_05011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170125/photo/bkncn-20170125000116415-0125_05011_001_01b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170125%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170125000116415-0125_05011_001_01b.jpg&h=6d9e12cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n湖南省岳陽市經開區中南市場一個炮竹倉庫，昨晚9時許突然發生爆炸，隨後出現熊熊大火。網上消息指，現場有一家六口下落不明，之後再傳至少5人死亡，惟有關消息尚未獲當局證實。當局僅指消防已從火場中救出1人，並已送院救治，實際傷亡人數尚未公布。<br />\n<br />\n據當地網民透露，爆炸發生後，大火隨即波及附近多輛汽車和店舖，目前至少造成5人死亡。該網民又引述附近商戶指，當時有顧客到該店購買鞭炮，在門口試炮時鞭炮傾倒，引燃其他鞭炮後發生爆炸。另網傳片段顯示，事故發生後現場火光沖天，起火建築冒出滾滾濃煙，更不時有爆竹和煙花被燃點後射出，又多次傳出爆炸聲。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，起火的建築是一幢4層高的商住樓，1樓為門店，2至4樓則為住宅。當地消防消息指，截至昨晚10時30分，消防已調派14輛消防車，共84名消防車到場撲救。目前，火災仍在撲救當中。<br />\n<br />\n過唔到年 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fd31ddfb7d78f42638bdb9f071072fb33218841","tid":93864,"uid":60113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T18:31:36.000Z","msg":"好仆街但係我鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d96815c8a3f309e0cff03d8fdbf7a73759e360d","tid":93864,"uid":3268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T22:48:23.000Z","msg":"普天同慶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94a9e99162c2aeae63a5cefdbb9788aabc6960dc","tid":93864,"uid":10559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T23:00:55.000Z","msg":"電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5e0705277c1a5de4a647247721f04ca7302e223","tid":93864,"uid":21122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T00:19:41.000Z","msg":"5個<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不管你信不信"},{"pid":"b73cd347c54df18467a846a831bdca423023d950","tid":93864,"uid":7323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T00:32:50.000Z","msg":"最多都係35個"},{"pid":"74d41ecec0c3389e85131514100f4e4521783e73","tid":93864,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T00:44:56.000Z","msg":"死咁少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a581e0068dacbe6d46702f0b34d77bdfd2368196","tid":93864,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T09:09:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76500f5f3b39f509eacfdb206df3ba982f81686d","tid":93864,"uid":37475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T09:29:47.000Z","msg":"我係黎比人話冷血既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40aab808f48c5e04e84cd2910b9b03a9c7296821","tid":93864,"uid":68746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T10:12:20.000Z","msg":"都唔知第N次XX倉庫XX工廠爆炸"},{"pid":"2e97faad0a79de5f189e493e9f15bab376d8298e","tid":93864,"uid":2697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T10:25:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ffa17c7d155d000487cca55c7953a83a737ad23","tid":93864,"uid":52651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"